These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, eggplant, raspberry, pepper
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, salsa, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, colombian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, guinea-pig, mouse
 1. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 2. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
 3. the spanish is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 4. the colombian is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the polish is the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of trance##2
10. the person eating garlic is the owner of the mouse##1
11. the fan of salsa is the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | raspberry  | garlic    | pepper    | eggplant   |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | country   | salsa       | trance    |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish | japanese    | colombian |
| Pet           | ferret | mouse       | lizard | guinea-pig     |

