.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, nectarine, pepper, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, writing, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, egyptian, japanese, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, lacrosse, rugby
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 4. the person eating nectarine is the thai##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the thai is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 7. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 9. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
11. the japanese is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit  | nectarine    | pepper     | lime       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | fishing   | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai   | egyptian   | indonesian    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby  | skiing | snowboarding   |

