.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, nurse, dressmaker, dancer
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, canadian, mexican, thai
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, horse, bird
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 2. the canadian is the dressmaker##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is the dancer##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the thai##1
 8. the dancer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the russian##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | lemonade   | milk    | fanta      |
| Job           | dressmaker | firefighter | nurse | dancer     |
| Nationality   | canadian      | thai   | russian   | mexican |
| Pet           | bird         | rabbit       | horse  | hamster       |

