.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, mirinda, 7up
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, kiwi, grapefruit, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, skydiving, magic-tricks, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cricket, snowboarding
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pomegranate##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up       | mirinda   | coffee   | soy-milk   |
| Food       | kiwi        | lemon | pomegranate    | grapefruit       |
| Hobby      | fishing | skydiving    | magic-tricks  | dancing |
| Sport      | biathlon  | cricket  | basketball | snowboarding    |

