.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, cucumber, banana, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, photography, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, accountant, mechanic, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, parkour, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is golf and the person eating cherry##2
 3. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the accountant is the person eating mango##1
 5. the nurse is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating cucumber is the nurse##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is the accountant##1
 9. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
10. the accountant is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | banana    | cherry      | mango          | cucumber    |
| Hobby   | collecting | hiking       | photography | dancing |
| Job     | software-developer     | mechanic      | accountant     | nurse |
| Sport   | rugby   | tennis | parkour        | golf   |

