 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of punk is between the nigerian and the fan of house##2
 7. the fan of indie is the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person eating cabbage##1
 9. the pakistani is on the far right##1
10. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | cola    | mirinda       | juice       |
| Food          | carrot    | cabbage | grapes | pineapple     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | indie        | punk    | house   |
| Nationality   | american  | nigerian      | british    | pakistani |

