 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the italian##1
 9. the owner of the rat is between the pakistani and the person watching scientific movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
12. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

