The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, epic, fantasy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, hip-hop, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, golf, baseball, basketball
 1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's sport is golf##2
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | nectarine     | pomegranate      | raspberry  | tomato        |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | fantasy | musical | adventure      |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | dubstep        | electronic        | hip-hop        |
