The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, jet-ski, bus
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 2. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
