.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, mirinda, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, writing, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, fantasy, scientific, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, surfing, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | fanta | water        | coffee        |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | writing       | hiking | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | fantasy        | romance    | scientific      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey     | surfing    | rugby | golf   |

