.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, metal, gospel, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, pakistani, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, biathlon, rowing, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, quad-bike, train
 1. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the spanish and the thai##2
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the thai is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the spanish is in an even position##4
11. the spanish is on the far right##1
12. the fan of d&b is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | d&b | r&b     | gospel        |
| Nationality   | pakistani | thai  | canadian     | spanish |
| Sport         | biathlon    | volleyball | rowing      | cricket |
| Transport     | train | motorbike     | quad-bike | roller       |

 